## 🚀 Quick Start

1. Refine product scope in `docs/PRD.md`
2. Pick a skill from `skills/` to guide your AI agent
3. Build source in `src/` with tests in `tests/`
4. Run `make test` to verify (TDD: red → green → refactor)
5. Repeat

## ⚙️ Development Commands

```bash
make test    # Run all tests
make lint    # Run linter
make build   # Build the project
```

## 🛠️ Development Principles

- Every change must keep this README and relevant `--help` text up to date.
- README and `--help` must describe what each command or feature produces (output artifacts).
- Prefer `make test` over manual test invocation.
